org.springframework.http.client

接口 AsyncClientHttpRequestFactory

  • 所有已知实现类:
    HttpComponentsAsyncClientHttpRequestFactory, InterceptingAsyncClientHttpRequestFactory, MockMvcClientHttpRequestFactory, Netty4ClientHttpRequestFactory, OkHttp3ClientHttpRequestFactory, SimpleClientHttpRequestFactory
    已过时。 
    as of Spring 5.0, in favor of ClientHttpConnector

    @Deprecated
public interface AsyncClientHttpRequestFactory
    Factory for AsyncClientHttpRequest objects. Requests are created by the createAsyncRequest(URI, HttpMethod) method.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Arjen Poutsma

    • 方法详细资料

      • createAsyncRequest

        AsyncClientHttpRequest createAsyncRequest(java.net.URI uri,
                                          HttpMethod httpMethod)
                                   throws java.io.IOException
        已过时。 
        Create a new asynchronous AsyncClientHttpRequest for the specified URI and HTTP method.

        The returned request can be written to, and then executed by calling AsyncClientHttpRequest.executeAsync().

        参数:
        uri - the URI to create a request for
        httpMethod - the HTTP method to execute
        返回:
        the created request
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - in case of I/O errors
